                     <interp inst="t18301028-173-person1478" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             had brought it to bake; I told him it would be done about nine; at a quarter before nine the prisoner came for it - I said it was not done, and would not be till nine; at five minutes past nine he came again, with a handkerchief, and had it - he paid me 1 1/2d. and took it away; I presumed he was one of the family.</p>
